      "id": "ae273a73_837079d8",
      "file_path": "policy-endpoints/pom.xml",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 70,
      "message": "I'm looking at the transitive dependencies on common-parameters since added here.   It introduces one with \"snakeyaml\" 1.21.   \n\nI also see in policy/models/pom.xml snakeyaml 1.18, and\n\n./models/models-interactions/model-yaml/pom.xml snakeyaml 1.17.\n\nAt runtime, the one that seems to \"win\" in the pdp-d is 1.18.\n\nWe should open a JIRA to clean out all these multiple versions of dependencies, fix them in policy/parent and do some regression tests.   I think Jim had some issue to migrate to 1.21 if I recall correctly in common-parameters, but it does not seem to get carried to runtime, at least in the pdp-d with all the versions.\n\nAgreement on open a JIRA on this?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 477,
        "name": "Jorge Hernandez",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jorge.hernandez-herrero@att.com",
        "username": "jhh"
      },
      "updated": "2019-06-26 15:27:39.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
